{"tid":1047260,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"話說當年中學有條友.....","createTime":"2019-03-04T23:47:17.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-04T23:47:17.000Z","uid":44954,"like":0,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"2a3b34a46c684c2e4c19235c3b387ed2ced00ff6","tid":1047260,"uid":44954,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-04T23:47:17.000Z","msg":"有一日去郊區考察，咁我地喺條橋附近見到好大嚿狗屎。咁大家都醒目，經過都特別小心。去到活動嘅尾聲，又去返個條橋附近，咁個同學A就見唔到嚿屎啦，但其實只係好近，應該唔中。之後係佢後面嘅同學B,同學們就話<br />\n對話如下:<br />\nB:喂！<br />\nA轉身問：咩事？<br />\nB:小心呀！<br />\nA:好呀！(轉返身)<br />\n之後A就一腳踢散咗嚿完整嘅屎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n個個都見到<br />\nA再轉身問:<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: blue;\">我係咪踢到嚿屎？</span></span></span><br />\nB,同學們:<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">冇呀冇呀</span><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}